description: This data set contains the current Molecular Analysis for Therapy Choice (MATCH) precision medcine clincal trial (Z1D) program data extracted from the NCI GDC. See https://www.cancer.gov/about-cancer/treatment/clinical-trials/nci-supported/nci-match for more information. The tables within this data set are dynamic and update with new releases; for static tables use CCLE_versioned.
